      "updated": 1767248242269,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1.计算ThreadLocal在Map中的初始索引",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "tLFwLr35CxmfcTODAF4lV",
      "originalText": "1.计算ThreadLocal在Map中的初始索引",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "JaBEHsWZ48JHZli-dkXgm",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 1108.4150588023463,
      "y": 524.1645911760456,
      "width": 1052,
      "height": 210,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#fff4e6",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "X6I9Mx4WrJLjzxe-fx5bf",
        "645_xPVozkkpTnqzuYRp0",
        "yNUGsdvPnChOlNr0B1J9o"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c6JN",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1789616065,
      "version": 484,
      "versionNonce": 1735131439,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [
        {
          "id": "Wgf5gPJ_xmTkTgRyXW6EZ",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ],
      "updated": 1767248242269,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false
    },
    {
      "id": "Wgf5gPJ_xmTkTgRyXW6EZ",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1113.4150588023463,
      "y": 529.1645911760456,
      "width": 1038.559814453125,
      "height": 200,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "X6I9Mx4WrJLjzxe-fx5bf",
        "645_xPVozkkpTnqzuYRp0",
        "yNUGsdvPnChOlNr0B1J9o"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c6JO",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 277594017,
      "version": 913,
      "versionNonce": 372452673,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1767248242269,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "代码执行流程：\nA. 首先还是根据key计算出索引 i，然后查找i位置上的Entry，\nB. 若是Entry已经存在并且key等于传入的key，那么这时候直接给这个Entry赋新的value值,\nC. 若是Entry存在，但是key为null，则调用replaceStaleEntry来更换这个key为空的Entry,\nD. 若Entry存在且Key！=当前key，不断循环检测，直到遇到为null的地方，这时候要是还没在循环过程中return，那么\n就在这个null的位置新建一个Entry，并且插入，同时size增加1。\nE.最后调用cleanSomeSlots，清理key为null的Entry，最后返回是否清理了Entry\nF.接下来再判断sz 是否>= thresgold达到了rehash的条件，达到的话就会调用rehash函数执行一次全表的扫描清理",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "JaBEHsWZ48JHZli-dkXgm",
      "originalText": "代码执行流程：\nA. 首先还是根据key计算出索引 i，然后查找i位置上的Entry，\nB. 若是Entry已经存在并且key等于传入的key，那么这时候直接给这个Entry赋新的value值,\nC. 若是Entry存在，但是key为null，则调用replaceStaleEntry来更换这个key为空的Entry,\nD. 若Entry存在且Key！=当前key，不断循环检测，直到遇到为null的地方，这时候要是还没在循环过程中return，那么就在这个null的位置新建一个Entry，并且插入，同时size增加1。\nE.最后调用cleanSomeSlots，清理key为null的Entry，最后返回是否清理了Entry\nF.接下来再判断sz 是否>= thresgold达到了rehash的条件，达到的话就会调用rehash函数执行一次全表的扫描清理",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "BVjUtmbLZLJIvMLUgyCbD",
